---
title: 表单校验流程图 (报销审批示例)
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    primaryColor: "#e8e8e6"
    primaryTextColor: "#1a1a1a"
    primaryBorderColor: "#8b8b8b"
    lineColor: "#6b7280"
    fontSize: 14
---
flowchart TD
    Input([Agent 收集的表单数据]) --> Required{所有必填字段<br/>非空?}
    
    Required -->|❌| Err1["errors: 'xxx 不能为空'"]
    Required -->|✅| Amount{金额 > 0<br/>且 ≤ 500000?}
    
    Amount -->|❌| Err2["errors: '金额范围错误'"]
    Amount -->|✅| Category{类别在枚举中?<br/>差旅费/办公用品/...}
    
    Category -->|❌| Err3["errors: '无效费用类别'"]
    Category -->|✅| Date{日期 ≤ 今天?}
    
    Date -->|❌| Err4["errors: '日期不能晚于今天'"]
    Date -->|✅| Pass["{ valid: true, errors: [] }"]
    
    Err1 --> Return[返回 ValidationResult 给 Agent]
    Err2 --> Return
    Err3 --> Return
    Err4 --> Return
    Pass --> Return
    Return --> Agent[Agent 根据 valid 决定<br/>继续提交或重新收集]
    
    style Input fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#6b7280,color:#1a1a1a
    style Pass fill:#f0fdf4,stroke:#6b7280,color:#1a1a1a
    style Err1 fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#6b7280,color:#1a1a1a
    style Err2 fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#6b7280,color:#1a1a1a
    style Err3 fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#6b7280,color:#1a1a1a
    style Err4 fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#6b7280,color:#1a1a1a